. Until next time, happy blogging!','Back-Linking: Just Do It!','','publish','open','open','','back-linking-just-do-it','','','2012-08-10 16:11:33','2012-08-10 16:11:33','',0,'http://www.markitmedia.com/blog/?p=209',0,'post','',0),(210,1,'2012-07-17 16:27:26','2012-07-17 16:27:26','What is Back-linking? Back-linking is the single most important important off-page SEO that someone can do. Back-linking is process of creating links to your website from other websites. They can be reciprocal or a one way link. The reason that this is important is that when a search engine rates a site\'s popularity, it does so by a measure of how many others sites link to it. The more site that link to yours, or back-links, the higher that site will appear in search results organically. One great way to build back-links is to list your site with online business directories. You can also ask other site to link to you in exchange for returning the favor. Building back-links is a long slow process, so don\'t get discouraged. A few months of dedicated work will payoff. Most importantly, don\'t stop. Also, do avoid link farming. Companies will offer services to build back-links. Some are good while others will hurt your site ranking by spamming your links. ','Back-linking: Just do it!','','inherit','open','open','','209-revision','','','2012-07-17 16:27:26','2012-07-17 16:27:26','',209,'http://www.markitmedia.com/blog/2012/07/209-revision/',0,'revision','',0),(211,1,'2012-07-17 16:28:08','2012-07-17 16:28:08','What is Back-linking? Back-linking is the single most important important off-page SEO that someone can do. Back-linking is process of creating links to your website from other websites. They can be reciprocal or a one way link. The reason that this is important is that when a search engine rates a site\'s popularity, it does so by a measure of how many others sites link to it. The more site that link to yours, or back-links, the higher that site will appear in search results organical