 Global Popularity, essentially ranking first in a Google search. How does one achieve this? Links from a popular website like, Facebook or Instagram are more significant. So having a link to Facebook, a hugely popular site, will have more of an impact than a company only posting links to their homepage.\r\n\r\n<strong>Local Popularity</strong>\r\n\r\nIn an effort to weed out websites full of span post that talk about actual locations became more relevant. This why in <a title=\"Markit Media \" href=\"http://instagram.com/markitmedia\" target=\"_blank\">Markit Medias Instagram</a> Contest the use of Camelback Mountain was so genius. Markit Media is located in Scottsdale, AZ they service businesses through out the country, but use the use of one of the most popular hiking spots in Arizona contribute revenant element to their Instagram Contest.\r\n\r\n<strong>Anchor Text</strong>\r\n\r\nOne of the strongest signals the search engines use in rankings. Anchor text is another term for keywords. When dozens of links point to a page with Keywords that relate to the links that will earn mayor SEO points.\r\n\r\n<strong>Trust Rank</strong>\r\n\r\nNot too surprising, the web has mass amounts of spam. As much as 60% of the internet is estimated to be spam! No one wants to sift through spam so Google weeds out irrelevant content with a link graph. This aspect takes time to build. Posting relevant links over a period of time will build up a companys trust rating.\r\n\r\n<strong>Freshness</strong>\r\n\r\nThis aspect is by far the funniest. Whats trending now? Social media is a fast moving beast that reflects the current pulse of our culture. You can serve up lots of loud, fun, fresh content!\r\n\r\nLet us know some tricks you have used in your most successful social posts.','Key Ways to Improve SEO Utilizing Social Media','','publish','open','open','','key-ways-to-improve-seo-utilizing-social-media','','','2014-09-18 22:24:39','2014-09-18 22:24:39','',0,'http://www.markitmedia.co